If you wanna play with this, keep in mind that everything is *highly experimental*.

PHP settings required:
	auto_globals_jit = Off
	
PHP settings suggested:
	log_errors = On
	error_log = /var/log/php_errors.log

Installation instruction:
	1. > git clone git://github.com/ettoredn/sephp-sandbox.git sephp-sandbox && cd sephp-sandbox
	2a. Debian users on a pristine Debian 6 installation
		> sudo ./install_debian.sh
	2b. Non-Debian users check what install_debian.sh does and adapt it to your system (sorry)
